<p>
Package <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/<%=pkg.name%>"><%=pkg.name%></a> has been updated and is now in version <strong><%=pkg.version%></strong>.

<% if(change_log_link){ %>
You can see the changelog <a href="<%=change_log_link%>">here</a>. 
<% }else{ %>
<%=pkg.name%> does not maintain a changelog, but you may find news about the version update <a href="https://github.com/<%=repo%>">here</a>.
<% } %>
</p> 

<p>
Cheers,<br/>
The <%=config.get('app.name')%> team
</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
